on (boxer)|Neil Simpson]]\n|{{abbr|RTD|Corner retirement}}\n|2 (8), {{small|3:00}}\n|6 Dec 2008\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[ExCeL]], London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|7\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|7\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[Lee Swaby]]\n|TKO\n|3 (8), {{small|2:45}}\n|26 Sep 2008\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|York Hall, London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|6\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|6\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Shawn McLean\n|TKO\n|6 (8), {{small|3:00}}\n|12 Sep 2008\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[Grosvenor House]], London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|5\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|5\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[Sam Sexton]]\n|TKO\n|6 (6), {{small|2:34}}\n|14 Jun 2008\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|York Hall, London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|4\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|4\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[Paul Butlin]]\n|PTS\n|4\n|12 Jan 2008\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|York Hall, London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|3\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|3\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} Darren Morgan\n|PTS\n|4\n|13 Oct 2007\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[York Hall]], London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|2\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|2\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} Tony Booth\n|{{abbr|PTS|Points decision}}\n|4\n|7 Apr 2007\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[Millennium Stadium]], [[Cardiff]], Wales}}\n|\n|-\n|1\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|1\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|HUN}} [[Istv\u00e1n Kecsk\u00e9s (boxer)|Istv\u00e1n Kecsk\u00e9s]]\n|{{abbr|TKO|Technical knockout}}\n|2 (4), {{small|1:21}}\n|17 Feb 2007\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[Wembley Arena]], [[London]], England}}\n|\n|}\n\n==Pay-per-view bouts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Date !! Fight !! Network !! [[Pay-per-view]] buys !! Source(s)\n|-\n| {{dts|2018|December|22|format=dmy}}\n| [[Dillian Whyte]] vs. Dereck Chisora II\n| [[Sky Box Office]]\n| 532,000\n| <ref name=\"boxingnewsandviews\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.barb.co.uk/viewing-data/weekly-viewing-summary/|title=Weekly viewing summary &#124; BARB}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2020|May|23|format=dmy}}\n| [[Oleksandr Usyk]] vs. Dereck Chisora\n| [[Sky Box Office]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|-\n|}\n\n==Filmography==\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class = \"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 2018\n| Pitbull: Last Dog\n| Boxer 2\n| \n|}\n\n==See also==\n{{Div col}}\n* [[List of European Boxing Union heavyweight champions]]\n* [[List of Commonwealth Boxing Council champions]]\n* [[List of British heavyweight boxing champions]]\n* [[List of ABA super-heavyweight champions]]\n{{Div col end}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Official website|http://www.delboychisora.com/}}\n*{{Boxrec|id=381739}}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-sports}}\n{{s-text|style=background:#C1D8FF; font-weight: bold;|text=Amateur boxing titles}}\n{{s-before|before=[[David Price (boxer)|David Price]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of ABA super-heavyweight champions|ABA super-heavyweight champion]]\n|years=2006}}\n{{s-after|after=David Price}}\n{{s-text|style=background:#C1D8FF; font-weight: bold;|text=Regional boxing titles}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Danny Williams (boxer)|Danny Williams]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of British heavyweight boxing champions|British heavyweight champion]]\n|years=15 May 2010 \u2013 23 July 2011}}\n{{s-aft|rows=4|after=[[Tyson Fury]]}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Sam Sexton]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of Commonwealth Boxing Council champions#Heavyweight|Commonwealth heavyweight champion]]\n|years=18 September 2010 \u2013 23 July 2011}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-vac|last=[[David Haye]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[World Boxing Organization|WBO]] International<br>heavyweight champion\n|years=20 July 2013 \u2013 29 November 2014}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-vac|last=[[Kubrat Pulev]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of European Boxing Union heavyweight champ